{"tid":2417294,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股災預言家警告：散戶沉醉泡沫之中　結局恐暴冧最少50%！","createTime":"2021-02-21T18:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T11:23:01.000Z","uid":215755,"like":115,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa53669d4c49684b15d3e166ff65c9240fb387d","tid":2417294,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T18:17:52.000Z","msg":"外媒報道，國際知名逆向投資者、曾準確預言過去兩次特大危機、被傳媒譽為「傳奇災難預言家」的GMO資產管理創辦人Jeremy Grantham再度發出警告，稱華爾街正處於泡沫之中，散戶也沉醉其中。<br />\n<br />\nJeremy Grantham指出，近幾個月來，股市的瘋狂和美股飆升正在演變成「史詩般的泡沫」，散戶變得欣喜若狂，四處借錢交易更多的股票。他又警告一直以來，牛市都會以泡沫破滅後下跌至少50%而告終，但引發這種暴跌的催化劑「難以預測」。<br />\n<br />\n然後，他表示，相較於美國市場，更喜歡新興市場資產，因為與定價過高的美國市場相比，新興市場的定價「相當合理」。儘管新興市場可能會與美國市場一同下跌，但由於新興市場價格較低，因此崩盤不會那麼嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210121/photo/bkn-20210121192156745-0121_00842_001_01p.jpg?20210122172914\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20210121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210121192156745-0121_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20210122172914&h=aefee74e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2fbaff54a48554f5263b23b671b4e69d9ae3ee8","tid":2417294,"uid":134522,"like":148,"dislike":0,"score":148,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T18:22:33.000Z","msg":"到時就知邊個無著褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27335602742e84c385e4c95fb91e71da935d178f","tid":2417294,"uid":304916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T18:24:05.000Z","msg":"祼泳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e51a9a05511b065099c8455029a9c8393f2a45e","tid":2417294,"uid":28181,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T18:25:39.000Z","msg":"特價時段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d246bbe4ffc9600cfd9202332a00d7cd6ec1b54","tid":2417294,"uid":113187,"l